N. petraeus Das and Kunte
, adult size up to 43.2 mm SVL (adult size up to 41.0 mm in
N. dattatreyaensis
); skin with close set of folds without any specific pattern (Fig 6 a, b & c) (skin corrugated with distinct pattern of three transverse folds, a dorsolateral fold and two lateral folds in
N. dattatreyaensis
